title: Candlelight in Algeria (1944, film) directed by George King

sources.title: Candlelight in Algeria (1944, film) directed by George King
sources.description:
Romance and Espionage in the Heart of War-Torn Algeria.
James Mason and Carla Lehmann star in this wartime British thriller about a fugitive British agent with a camera full of secrets been hidden from Nazi spies by a beautiful sculptress.

Original title: Candlelight in Algeria (1944)
Subtitles are available in many languages.


Colorized version: https://youtu.be/MiC30pGUKCU


Director: George King
Producers: George King, John Stafford
Writers: Brock Williams, Katherine Strueby, Dorothy Hope, John Clements
Stars: James Mason, Carla Lehmann, Raymond Lovell
Genres: Classics, Drama, History, War
